values:
it's the first day of classes for my winter term and i already want it to be christmas break. it probably doesn't help that sarah and i decorated our room with lights and a christmas tree. oy.

so, i have a different german professor, and i don't like her as much as my old one. but i have a really cool anthro class about africa. and, oh! first ghana seminar! so excited.....although it was about all the shots and diseases we could get.

and i have a headache. my eyes hurt. my brain hurts. i need to sleep. someone needs to rescue me from the evil that is school.

ok, so i have been informed by a certain little someone to make sure everyone knows she is the only one who can call me "katie batie." if she catches anyone calling me that, i am afraid she might kill you with a spoon....or some other blunt utensil.
yeah. zam made me create an account. don't know how much i'll use this. we'll see. but i do like my picture. hehehe.
